<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="simplify-vt">simplify <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sɪmplɪfaɪ/    美 /'sɪmplɪfaɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>简化：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Although I was young I could simplify difficult sums.
尽管那时还小，但我能简化复杂的算术题。</p><footer>人教② – 3</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>While intelligent people can often <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (simple) the complex, a fool is more likely to complicate the simple.  （2013 湖北）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. simplify  </p></div>